<div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header text-center">
                <h3 class="mb-0"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i><%= title %></h3>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body text-center py-5">
                <div class="mb-4">
                    <% if (title.includes('404')) { %>
                        <i class="fas fa-map-signs fa-5x text-warning"></i>
                    <% } else if (title.includes('500')) { %>
                        <i class="fas fa-server fa-5x text-danger"></i>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle fa-5x text-primary"></i>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
                
                <h4 class="mb-3"><%= message %></h4>
                
                <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                    <% if (title.includes('404')) { %>
                        抱歉，您尋找的頁面可能已被移動、刪除或暫時無法使用。
                    <% } else if (title.includes('500')) { %>
                        伺服器發生內部錯誤，請稍後再試或聯繫系統管理員。
                    <% } else { %>
                        發生未預期的錯誤，請稍後再試。
                    <% } %>
                </p>
                
                <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-center">
                    <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-outline-primary me-md-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>返回上一頁
                    </a>
                    <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>返回首頁
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="card-footer text-center">
                <small class="text-muted">
                    如需進一步協助，請聯繫系統管理員或參考<a href="/help">使用說明</a>。
                </small>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card mt-4">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">常見問題解決方法</h5>
                <div class="accordion" id="errorAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#errorOne">
                                頁面不存在 (404)
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="errorOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#errorAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>檢查網址是否正確</li>
                                    <li>確認您有存取該頁面的權限</li>
                                    <li>頁面可能已被移動或刪除</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#errorTwo">
                                伺服器錯誤 (500)
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="errorTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#errorAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>請稍後再試，可能是暫時性問題</li>
                                    <li>清除瀏覽器快取和 Cookie</li>
                                    <li>聯繫系統管理員報告問題</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#errorThree">
                                權限不足
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="errorThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#errorAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>確認您已登入系統</li>
                                    <li>檢查您的使用者角色是否有足夠權限</li>
                                    <li>聯繫管理員申請權限</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>